'''三氟化银'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为AgF<sub>3</sub>。其晶体结构与[[三氟化金|AuF<sub>3</sub>]]十分相似，它的AgF<sub>4</sub>通过氟桥连接形成链状聚合物。<ref>{{cite journal | title=Silver Trifluoride: Preparation, Crystal Structure, Some Properties, and Comparison with AuF<sub>3</sub> | journal=J Am Chem Soc |year=1991 | volume=113 | pages=4192–4198 | doi=10.1021/ja00011a021| last1=Zemva | first1=Boris | last2=Lutar | first2=Karel | last3=Jesih | first3=Adolf | last4=Casteel | first4=William J. | last5=Wilkinson | first5=Angus P. | last6=Cox | first6=David E. | last7=von Dreele | first7=Robert B. | last8=Borrmann | first8=Horst | last9=Bartlett | first9=Neil | issue=11 }}</ref>

== 制备 ==
三氟化银可由含AgF<sub>4</sub><sup>−</sup>离子的溶液在无水[[氟化氢|氟化氢]]中和[[三氟化硼|三氟化硼]]反应得到。它在无水氟化氢中室温时，会自发分解为Ag<sub>3</sub>F<sub>8</sub>。早期使用[[二氟化氪|二氟化氪]]作为氟化剂的制备方法倾向于生成混合价态的Ag<sub>3</sub>F<sub>8</sub>。

除了[[三氟化硼|三氟化硼]]外，[[四氟化锗|四氟化锗]]也能作为F<sup>−</sup>受体制备三氟化银：<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Fluorine Chemistry|volume=89|issue=1|language=en|date=1998-04|pages=101–104|doi=10.1016/S0022-1139(98)00093-1|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022113998000931|title=High yield room temperature syntheses of KAgF4 and AgF3 and the preparation and unit cell of LiAgF4|accessdate=2021-01-20|author=G.M. Lucier, J.M. Whalen, N. Bartlett|archive-date=2018-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180603174308/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022113998000931}}</ref>
: 2 AgF<sub>4</sub><sup>−</sup> + GeF<sub>4</sub> → 2 AgF<sub>3</sub> + GeF<sub>6</sub><sup>2−</sup>

三氟化银也能由[[二氟化二氧|二氟化二氧]]在[[五氟化氯|五氟化氯]]中和金属[[银|银]]反应得到。<ref>Kiselev, Yu. M.; Popov, A. I.; Timakov, A. A.; Bukharin, K. V.; Sukhoverkhov, V. F. Several properties of higher binary silver fluorides. ''Zhurnal Neorganicheskoi Khimii'', 1988. 33 (5): 1252-1256. ISSN: 0044-457X.</ref>

